graph LR
    KServe[KServe Operator<br/>Controller + Webhook]

    %% External Platform Dependencies
    KServe -->|serverless<br/>autoscaling| Knative[Knative Serving<br/>v1.x<br/>Optional]
    KServe -->|traffic mgmt<br/>mTLS| Istio[Istio<br/>1.x<br/>Optional]
    KServe -->|custom metrics<br/>autoscaling| KEDA[KEDA<br/>v2.x<br/>Optional]
    KServe -->|webhook certs| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>v1.x<br/>Optional]
    KServe -->|metrics scraping| Prometheus[Prometheus Operator<br/>v1<br/>Optional]
    KServe -->|LLM tracing| OpenTelemetry[OpenTelemetry Operator<br/>v1beta1<br/>Optional]
    KServe -->|ingress alt| GatewayAPI[Gateway API<br/>v1<br/>Optional]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    KServe -->|API calls<br/>gRPC/9090| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>Internal ODH]
    KServe -.->|mTLS sidecars| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>Internal RHOAI]
    ODHOperator[OpenDataHub Operator<br/>Internal ODH] -->|enables/disables<br/>DataScienceCluster| KServe
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Internal ODH] -->|creates<br/>InferenceServices| KServe
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Internal ODH] -.->|auto deploy| KServe

    %% External Storage Services
    KServe -->|model storage<br/>HTTPS/443| S3[S3 Storage<br/>AWS/MinIO/Ceph]
    KServe -->|model storage<br/>HTTPS/443| GCS[Google Cloud Storage<br/>GCP]
    KServe -->|model storage<br/>HTTPS/443| Azure[Azure Blob Storage<br/>Azure]

    %% Platform Dependencies
    KServe -->|CRD watches<br/>creates resources| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    KServe -.->|request/response<br/>logging| EventBroker[Event Broker<br/>Knative Eventing<br/>Optional]

    %% Integration Points (reverse direction - who uses KServe)
    subgraph "Consumers of KServe"
        UserWorkloads[User Applications] -->|inference requests<br/>HTTP/gRPC| KServe
        NotebookServers[Jupyter Notebooks<br/>Internal ODH] -->|KServe SDK<br/>Python API| KServe
    end

